All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<AbstractTrigger>
public class AutoConfigureTrigger
extends AbstractConfigurableTrigger

This class implements triggers that trigger an auto configure functionality.

AutoConfigureTriggers show up in the auto configure toolbar repsectivly in the auto configure dialog and can be called from the commandline.

The run(Map) method of the AutoConfigureTrigger does not show up the dialog of the wizard but directly runs the auto configure operation.
